title: betty
description:
This is the trilogy, the trifecta, the final chapter of this love triangle between Betty, James and Augustine.. This is from the view of James, the boy who was foolish! What did Taylor have to say about this song? And who did she hear first singing it? And why does that question make Nick go into total guy mode? Listen to find out!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
